---
// Features section showcasing ColorClip Pro capabilities
---

<section class="features section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="phosphor-glow" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
      Everything you need for professional color work
    </h2>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <!-- Feature 1: Unlimited Palettes -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
┌─────────┐
│ ▓ ▓ ▓ ▓ │
│ ▓ ▓ ▓ ▓ │
│ ▓ ▓ ▓ ▓ │
└─────────┘
        </pre>
        <h3>Unlimited Palettes</h3>
        <p>
          Create and organize up to 256 swatches per palette. Name, label,
          and track color history for each swatch.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 2: Screen Eyedropper -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
   ╭───╮
   │ ◉ │
   │ │ │
   ╰─┼─╯
     ▼
        </pre>
        <h3>Screen Eyedropper</h3>
        <p>
          Pick colors from anywhere on your screen with pixel-perfect precision.
          Works across all applications.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 3: Cloud Sync -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
  ☁  ↕  ☁
     │
  ┌──┴──┐
  │█████│
  └─────┘
        </pre>
        <h3>Cloud Sync</h3>
        <p>
          Sync palettes across all your devices in real-time. Sign in with
          Google, GitHub, or Discord.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 4: All Color Formats -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
#FF5733
RGB(255…)
HSV(11…)
α: 0.80
        </pre>
        <h3>All Color Formats</h3>
        <p>
          Work with HEX, RGB, HSV, and normalized values. Copy in any format
          with a single click.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 5: Intuitive Color Picker -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
    ╭───╮
   ╱ ◉ ◉ ╲
  │ ◉ ● ◉ │
   ╲ ◉ ◉ ╱
    ╰───╯
        </pre>
        <h3>Intuitive Picker</h3>
        <p>
          Choose between color wheel or slider-based picking. Full alpha
          channel support for transparency.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 6: Multi-language -->
      <article class="feature-card">
        <pre class="feature-icon">
┌───────────┐
│ EN FR DE  │
│ ES IT RU  │
│ JA KO ZH  │
└───────────┘
        </pre>
        <h3>9 Languages</h3>
        <p>
          Available in English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Russian,
          Korean, Japanese, and Chinese.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--phosphor-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--phosphor-dim);
  }

  .features h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid var(--phosphor-dim);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all var(--anim-normal);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--phosphor-green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--phosphor-glow);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--phosphor-green);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--phosphor-green);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    }
  }

  /* Accessibility: Reduced motion */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .feature-card {
      transition: none;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
